pageHeader: Explore the latest shoes for men for every sport, workout and everyday look. Built for ultimate performance and sneaker style, Nike shoes for men deliver cutting-edge technologies specific to your sport in iconic designs.
shoeInfoBodyOne: Engineered for the strongest player on the court, the LeBron 16 Basketball Shoe delivers a powerful combination of support, impact cushioning and instant responsiveness. The tongue and lacing allow for easy entry and a custom fit, so you can lock in when needed and wear loose when you want.
shoeInfoBodyTwo: BattleKnit 2.0 is Flyknit designed specifically for LeBron. Itâ€™s lightweight, ultra-strong, and supportive exactly where you need it.
shoeInfoBodyThree: Combined Max Air and Zoom Air cushioning system helps absorb impact from hard landings then bounces back with explosive energy return. It is articulated to keep it flexible up and down the court.
title: LeBron 16
subtitle: Basketball Shoe

shoeInfoBodyOne: The Kyrie 4 Men's Basketball Shoe is ultra-flexible, responsive and supportive. It's designed for Kyrie Irving's sudden changes of direction and smooth yet rapid playing style.
shoeInfoBodyTwo: The Flex Groove outsole has a zigzag cutout along the bottom for excellent flexibility and traction. The sides of the sole are curved to enable smooth transitions and fast, fluid play.
shoeInfoBodyThree: Under your foot is lightweight foam with Nike Zoom Air cushioning in the heel. It provides soft comfort and a responsive feel with every move.
title: Kyrie 4
subtitle: Basketball Shoe
